task.summary: Default task
Updated implementation notes
Fix clip_property for tracker notes and type spec for both notes and rcording
Add missing clip_property for duration
A variety of changes to get to where generated documentation passes and all other unit tests pass as well.
IDE changes
IDE changes in support of documentation match.
Rearrange directory structure to match camdkit.
Rearrange directory structure to match camdkit.
Rearrange directory structure to match camdkit.
Allow a few userful arithmetic operations on Rational and StrictlyPositiveRational objects
Adjust import forwarding contents of model.py and framework.py
Copy over various files from classic camdkit to aid in compatibility testing
Comment out print statement.
Add mechanism to add properties from outside the Clip definition itself.
Refactor out schema traversal so we can use it for property setup.
Reorder definitions for clarity; remove print statements.
Use type hints to find the model classes required to add properties to Clip programmatically rather than in the current boilerplate.
Generate rather than hand-code all those properties of Clip that reach down into the nested CompatibleBaseModels.
Remove 638 lines of commented-out hand-rolled property definitions.
Clip.append() and a unit test for it.
Get rid of everything in derived_artifacts except the (not completed, thus not used) summarize_constraints() function.
Add ability to supply an argument to example generators to redirect output to a file
Add missing default of None for Synchronization frequency.
Compatibility "as" imports, plus get rid of parentId.
Comment out a bunch of print statements.
Add Clip.__getitem__() to support indexing (dubious as that practice may be).
Get rid of an "additionalProperties": False at Clip top-level to match classic camdkit at that level.
Change example that was passing physical dimensions to indicate the size in sensels of the active sensor area.
Sort keys when outputting JSON for easier comparison with other implementations (e.g. classic).
Rework protocol versioning so that generated schema matches that of classic camdkit.
Restore accidentally dropped frequency component of Synchronization
Reset version back to compatible 0,9,1
Add aggregate target to generate all example output into /tmp
Add aggregate target to generate all example output into /tmp
Add aggregate target to generate all example output into /tmp
Add aggregate target to generate all example output into /tmp
Enhance the URN UUID generifier in test_examples.py such that it can handle URNs buried lower down (e.g. the fdlLink URN UUID in camera static)
Add a bunch more tests for timecode format, including sub_frames
Workspace changes to support the above
Changes to not-to-be-published notes and experiments
Bring over make_opentrackio_documentation.py from classic camdkit
Bring over OpenTrackIO.html from classic camdkit
Add a bunch of files so we can build OpenTrackIO doc in-tree.
Revert to classic camdkit generate_x_y_example.py and associated XML files; add test_example_regression.py to compare out generated schema against that of classic.
Switch the main model_dump in CompatibleBaseModel's to_json() over to use exclude_defaults=True
Add test to make sure we handle a non-default sub_frame OK. Mild gestures at PEP8 cleanup (there is a LOT to do).
Workspace changes reflecting recent addition of resources and reorganization of tools
Update to use setuptools; update README.md "State of the implementation" section.
Change references from PTP master to PTP leader
